item.title: The Lord is Good: Psalm 103
item.description: Today's speaker is Dr. Thomas White, President of Cedarville University. Speaking from Psalm 103, Dr. White urges us to praise the Lord with every fiber of our being. Feed: https://mediaserve.cedarville.edu/ChapelMedia/data/podcast?id=president

item.title: Root Cause
item.description:
This week, Michael Marshall joins us for a skeptical review of Root Cause, a documentary that claims virtually all medical maladies arise from root canals. And then gets taken off Netflix super-duper quick because that's nonsense.
